  ID: MalteseSoldier
  Name: Salvatore
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Crushed under collapsing stone during bombardment, ribs broken,
    breath shallow.\n\nStory: Salvatore, a stonemason who built parts of Fort St.
    Elmo, lies pinned beneath the rubble of his own craft. He wheezes that the walls
    he raised with his bare hands have betrayed him, killing him as surely as the
    enemy\u2019s cannon. His sons once helped him carry stone \u2014 he fears they
    will die under it too before this siege is over.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal:
    2"
  slotNumber: 2
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 2
